snippet.title: Amberz Asylum
snippet.description:
At the age of 15 I had a negative attachment that left me with more quesions than answers. 

Today,  I work to show people the real side of the paranormal. Alot of people only know what they see on TV. And often times what you see on TV isnt exactly reality. I work to help educate people about the paranormal and hopefully, set the basis for a world that accepts spirits as fact.
